$ VBA statement: dim
@ dim

The `dim` statement allows to declare the → development/languages/VBA/language/datatypes[data type] of variables.
-
Don't confuse `dim` with → development/languages/VBA/language/statements/declare[`declare`].

The `option explicit` statement ensures that variables are declared with a `dim` statement.


sa:
  → development/languages/VBA/language/statements
